      ],
      "source": "https://nanuetchamber.com/about-nanuet/"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "The New Jersey & New York Railroad arrived in Nanuet in 1869, later becoming the Pascack Valley Line that still serves the town.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        11,
        12
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia",
        "Web source 1"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nanuet%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "The Shops at Nanuet, an outdoor mall opened in 1969 and rebranded in 2013, is operated by Simon Property Group.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        5,
