      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nanuet%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Nanuet station ranks as the second‑to‑last stop on New Jersey Transit’s Pascack Valley Line, connecting to Hoboken Terminal.",
